    <sense group="1" n="1" name="the acquisition of something with money" type="Event">
        <commentary>
            PURCHASE[+event][+contractual][+acquisition][+with_money]
            the acquisition of something for payment
            Note: a nominalization: X's purchase of Y -&gt; X purchased Y
        </commentary>
        <examples>
            They have a large selection of videos available for purchase. (X purchase them)
            The purchase of that large tract of North America was made during the Napoleonic Wars.
            The courts may rule that purchase of the smaller company by the larger is monopolistic.
        </examples>
        <mappings>
            <wn version="2.0">1</wn>
            <omega/>
            <pb>purchase.01</pb>
        </mappings>
        <SENSE_META clarity=""/>
    </sense>
    
    <sense group="1" n="2" name="thing bought" type="">
